01:00:01.630 --> 01:00:01.640
vertical—that

01:00:01.640 --> 01:00:03.230
he doesn't go horizontal and get

01:00:03.240 --> 01:00:04.470
prideful

01:00:04.480 --> 01:00:06.470
with the power that God's bestowed upon

01:00:06.480 --> 01:00:07.910
him

01:00:07.920 --> 01:00:11.430
to have the most powerful military

01:00:11.440 --> 01:00:13.590
in the world,

01:00:13.600 --> 01:00:15.670
to have whatever he needs at his

01:00:15.680 --> 01:00:16.910
fingertips,

01:00:16.920 --> 01:00:22.150
but to always keep vertical.

01:00:22.160 --> 01:00:24.950
Trump needs to keep vertical.

01:00:24.960 --> 01:00:27.790
And that's why I told you the Lord said,

01:00:27.800 --> 01:00:31.510
'I will hold the church accountable

01:00:31.520 --> 01:00:34.550
for these blocks that are on his feet to

01:00:34.560 --> 01:00:37.430
get him across the finish

01:00:37.430 --> 01:00:37.440
line.'And

01:00:37.440 --> 01:00:39.350
how do we do that? By praying for

01:00:39.360 --> 01:00:40.470
him—that

01:00:40.480 --> 01:00:42.590
he doesn't go horizontal, that he

01:00:42.590 --> 01:00:42.600
doesn't

01:00:42.600 --> 01:00:44.270
start looking at himself as

01:00:44.280 --> 01:00:46.750
something that he's not, a God figure.

01:00:46.760 --> 01:00:49.030
He is not Jesus in the photo and

01:00:49.040 --> 01:00:50.230
everybody wants to defend it. 'Brandon,

01:00:50.240 --> 01:00:52.910
you're wrong.'No, out of the heart.

01:00:52.920 --> 01:00:54.790
There's things there that the Lord said

01:00:54.800 --> 01:00:56.150
you don't know.

01:00:56.160 --> 01:00:58.270
And I'm not here as a prophetic

01:00:58.280 --> 01:01:02.030
voice, as a watchman to warn you; you

01:01:02.040 --> 01:01:04.790
are naive to what the Lord is telling

01:01:04.800 --> 01:01:07.350
me. A root of pride is trying to step

01:01:07.360 --> 01:01:09.550
in.

01:01:09.560 --> 01:01:11.150
And the only way you're ever going to

01:01:11.160 --> 01:01:12.430
get there, with Franklin Graham and all

01:01:12.440 --> 01:01:13.710
these people coming out and saying how

01:01:13.720 --> 01:01:15.950
great he is... I believe he's

01:01:15.960 --> 01:01:17.790
a great guy. Yeah, he has flesh. We all

01:01:17.800 --> 01:01:19.030
have flesh.

01:01:19.040 --> 01:01:20.870
But the Lord said to keep the main thing

01:01:20.880 --> 01:01:23.270
the main thing and always go

01:01:23.280 --> 01:01:24.430
vertical.

01:01:24.440 --> 01:01:26.550
Keep your eyes on Him. And what does

01:01:26.560 --> 01:01:29.590
that entail for the church? To keep

01:01:29.590 --> 01:01:29.600
ourselves

01:01:29.600 --> 01:01:33.030
on our knees that we pray

01:01:33.040 --> 01:01:36.310
for him. We don't idolize or worship.

01:01:36.320 --> 01:01:38.030
'Oh, Trump's the greatest! Trump, Trump,

01:01:38.030 --> 01:01:38.040
Trump!'No,

01:01:38.040 --> 01:01:40.710
Jesus is the greatest.

01:01:40.720 --> 01:01:43.070
Jesus, Jesus, Jesus. And we thank you,

01:01:43.080 --> 01:01:44.870
Lord,

01:01:44.880 --> 01:01:48.030
that we have a man after your own heart

01:01:48.040 --> 01:01:50.470
that will lead this

01:01:50.470 --> 01:01:50.480
nation—one

01:01:50.480 --> 01:01:54.230
nation under God.

01:01:54.240 --> 01:01:55.910
Under God,

01:01:55.920 --> 01:01:57.990
not under Trump. Under God. 'Well,

01:01:58.000 --> 01:02:00.030
Brandon, that's

01:02:00.030 --> 01:02:00.040
obvious.'No,

01:02:00.040 --> 01:02:02.310
it's not obvious to a lot of you. We

01:02:02.320 --> 01:02:05.030
get the emails.

01:02:05.040 --> 01:02:06.670
Regardless of Sister Clipboard

01:02:06.680 --> 01:02:07.910
out there going, 'Man, you're not

01:02:07.920 --> 01:02:09.150
