01:02:09.160 --> 01:02:10.910
keyboard warrior. I may not be talking to

01:02:10.920 --> 01:02:12.030
you,

01:02:12.040 --> 01:02:13.910
or maybe I am.

01:02:13.920 --> 01:02:16.070
But you need to get off your high horse

01:02:16.080 --> 01:02:17.910
and think about what I'm saying instead

01:02:17.920 --> 01:02:19.350
of typing away on your keyboard, always

01:02:19.360 --> 01:02:21.590
judging me. I'm trying to tell you, get

01:02:21.600 --> 01:02:24.070
on your face before a holy

01:02:24.080 --> 01:02:27.110
God and seek Him, and He will direct this

01:02:27.120 --> 01:02:29.070
path. He will direct Trump. He will do

01:02:29.080 --> 01:02:30.870
all that we need to do in the spirit

01:02:30.880 --> 01:02:34.630
realm. If we seek Jesus—'If my

01:02:34.640 --> 01:02:36.270
people

01:02:36.280 --> 01:02:38.990
who are called by my name will humble

01:02:39.000 --> 01:02:41.270
themselves and pray

01:02:41.280 --> 01:02:44.030
and turn from their wicked

01:02:44.030 --> 01:02:44.040
ways'—then

01:02:44.040 --> 01:02:46.510
who will heal our land?

01:02:46.520 --> 01:02:48.390
Jesus.

01:02:48.400 --> 01:02:50.630
He will fix it.

01:02:50.640 --> 01:02:52.030
He's the one that's going to

01:02:52.040 --> 01:02:54.310
fix all this. Will he use Trump to do

01:02:54.320 --> 01:02:55.950
it? If that's what he

01:02:55.960 --> 01:02:59.870
wants to do. He could use you.

01:02:59.880 --> 01:03:01.870
Doesn't mean he has to use Trump.

01:03:01.880 --> 01:03:04.790
He can use whoever says, 'I am here,

01:03:04.800 --> 01:03:08.350
Lord, use me. Send

01:03:08.350 --> 01:03:08.360
me.'Some

01:03:08.360 --> 01:03:10.350
plant, some water, but God

01:03:10.360 --> 01:03:12.790
always brings forth the increase.

01:03:12.800 --> 01:03:14.710
It's not you who brings it, and neither

01:03:14.720 --> 01:03:15.950
is it Trump.

01:03:15.960 --> 01:03:17.670
It's Jesus.

01:03:17.680 --> 01:03:19.070
He will bring forth the increase in

01:03:19.080 --> 01:03:20.990
these end times.

01:03:21.000 --> 01:03:23.270
Jesus will. He will bring forth the

01:03:23.280 --> 01:03:24.910
repentance. He will do this. But it's

01:03:24.920 --> 01:03:27.190
through the church praying

01:03:27.200 --> 01:03:30.990
and not exalting a man. He is not Caesar

01:03:32.200 --> 01:03:34.830
Augustus. He is not

01:03:36.000 --> 01:03:39.670
whatever.

01:03:39.680 --> 01:03:42.110
We always need to give Jesus all

01:03:42.120 --> 01:03:44.190
the praise, and He will change the heart

01:03:44.200 --> 01:03:46.350
of Pharaohs. He

01:03:46.360 --> 01:03:48.310
has the heart of the king; the Bible says

01:03:48.320 --> 01:03:49.790
the heart of the king is in the hand of

01:03:49.800 --> 01:03:52.630
the Lord.

01:03:52.640 --> 01:03:55.270
So we pray for Donald Trump. We lift up

01:03:55.280 --> 01:03:56.870
his family.

01:03:56.880 --> 01:03:59.470
We lift up his marriage. The Lord said

01:03:59.480 --> 01:04:02.630
specifically pray over his marriage. The

01:04:02.640 --> 01:04:04.310
Lord said specifically pray for the

01:04:04.320 --> 01:04:07.790
safety of his kids and his grandkids.

01:04:07.800 --> 01:04:09.550
That's our job.

01:04:09.560 --> 01:04:11.150
Would I love to meet him one day

01:04:11.160 --> 01:04:12.630
and give him a hug and say, 'Great job,

01:04:12.640 --> 01:04:14.990
you're a good guy, man'?

01:04:15.000 --> 01:04:16.430
Just give you a hug. Do I

01:04:16.440 --> 01:04:17.870
agree with everything that you've done?

01:04:17.880 --> 01:04:19.870
No. But it's a lot better than Bush,

01:04:19.880 --> 01:04:21.430
it's a lot better than Obama, and

01:04:21.440 --> 01:04:24.990
it's certainly better than the Clintons.

01:04:25.000 --> 01:04:26.750
So we just go, "Hey God, this is who

01:04:26.760 --> 01:04:28.790
we have in there."We pray for him to get

01:04:28.800 --> 01:04:30.990
across the finish line,

01:04:31.000 --> 01:04:34.030
but he is not a deity.

01:04:34.040 --> 01:04:36.150
Kim prophesied, Brandon. That's how many

01:04:36.160 --> 01:04:38.790
times Kim prophesied.

01:04:38.800 --> 01:04:40.670
I'm not rebutting what Kim

01:04:40.680 --> 01:04:42.470
Clement prophesied.

01:04:42.480 --> 01:04:45.710
I love Kim Clement. I love his

01:04:45.720 --> 01:04:46.750
family.

01:04:46.760 --> 01:04:48.990
I'm not rebutting that. I'm trying to

01:04:49.000 --> 01:04:51.510
tell you that regardless of what Kim

01:04:51.520 --> 01:04:53.750
Clement prophesied, it won't happen

01:04:53.760 --> 01:04:57.710
unless you pray him through it.

01:04:57.720 --> 01:05:01.390
Prophecy is free will.

01:05:02.440 --> 01:05:04.310
You can prophesy over me all day long

01:05:04.320 --> 01:05:05.430
and say, "Brandon, you're going to do

01:05:05.440 --> 01:05:06.990
this and you're going to do

01:05:06.990 --> 01:05:07.000
that."But

01:05:07.000 --> 01:05:09.870
it's my free will to do it. Prophecies

01:05:09.880 --> 01:05:14.190
don't force you to do something;

01:05:14.200 --> 01:05:15.870
you still have free will.

01:05:15.880 --> 01:05:17.590
And it's still our job as a church to

01:05:17.600 --> 01:05:18.910
pray for him.

01:05:18.920 --> 01:05:21.230
Regardless of Kim Clement, R.W.

01:05:21.230 --> 01:05:21.240
Schambach,

01:05:21.240 --> 01:05:23.590
or whoever prophesied,

01:05:23.600 --> 01:05:27.470
I don't care. As I said,

01:05:27.480 --> 01:05:29.510
we all can miss it. As

01:05:29.520 --> 01:05:31.550
much as I love Kim Clement, I'm sure he

01:05:31.560 --> 01:05:33.470
can miss it. And if he was here today,

01:05:33.480 --> 01:05:34.870
he'd probably tell you the same thing:

01:05:34.880 --> 01:05:37.590
"Hey, I missed it before."Have I missed it before?

01:05:37.600 --> 01:05:40.070
Is he a deity?

01:05:40.080 --> 01:05:42.230
No. He's a man just like Brandon Biggs.

01:05:42.240 --> 01:05:44.470
He's a man just like anybody else. Can

01:05:44.480 --> 01:05:47.310
Kim Clement miss it? I'm sure he could.

01:05:47.320 --> 01:05:50.750
Do I know that he has? I don't.

01:05:50.760 --> 01:05:52.190
I told his daughter, "I believe

01:05:52.200 --> 01:05:53.350
he's one of the most accurate prophets

01:05:53.360 --> 01:05:57.990
of this

01:05:57.990 --> 01:05:58.000
generation."And

01:05:58.000 --> 01:05:59.590
I still stand by that.

01:05:59.600 --> 01:06:02.550
Now, do we always try to

01:06:02.560 --> 01:06:04.470
make his words fit when we think they

01:06:04.480 --> 01:06:06.870
should fit? Yeah, people do.

01:06:06.880 --> 01:06:08.310
He's not here to defend

01:06:08.320 --> 01:06:09.830
himself;

01:06:09.840 --> 01:06:11.510
the Lord took him home.

01:06:11.520 --> 01:06:12.790
He's gone.

01:06:12.800 --> 01:06:15.270
But where one general

01:06:15.280 --> 01:06:17.390
goes home, God raises up a new one

01:06:17.390 --> 01:06:17.400
and

01:06:17.400 --> 01:06:19.230
says, "Finish the

01:06:19.240 --> 01:06:20.710
race."And

01:06:20.720 --> 01:06:22.550
if that general goes home, God will

01:06:22.560 --> 01:06:24.190
raise up another one and say, "Finish

01:06:24.200 --> 01:06:26.230
the race.

01:06:26.240 --> 01:06:28.150
Run."It

01:06:28.160 --> 01:06:30.030
doesn't mean the job's done.

01:06:30.040 --> 01:06:32.910
When a major soldier dies on

01:06:32.920 --> 01:06:35.110
