01:06:35.120 --> 01:06:36.830
soldier to grab the gun and keep

01:06:36.840 --> 01:06:38.110
going.

01:06:38.120 --> 01:06:39.390
And that's what we're seeing with this

01:06:39.400 --> 01:06:42.070
generation. He went home in 2015. God's

01:06:42.080 --> 01:06:46.270
raising up new voices.

01:06:46.280 --> 01:06:47.910
And that's what happens; it's called the

01:06:47.920 --> 01:06:50.630
cycle of life.

01:06:50.640 --> 01:06:54.230
So, we don't idolize people.

01:06:54.240 --> 01:06:56.390
The moment you start idolizing people

01:06:56.400 --> 01:06:58.230
instead of the Lord Jesus Christ, you're

01:06:58.240 --> 01:07:00.430
on the wrong road.

01:07:00.440 --> 01:07:02.230
I have to correct that a little bit

01:07:02.240 --> 01:07:03.310
tonight. There

01:07:03.310 --> 01:07:03.320
are

01:07:03.320 --> 01:07:05.270
so many of you who are on the

01:07:05.280 --> 01:07:09.550
wrong road. Look to Jesus.

01:07:09.560 --> 01:07:12.870
Stop idolizing prophetic voices. Stop

01:07:12.880 --> 01:07:14.430
idolizing

01:07:14.440 --> 01:07:16.710
ministers, presidents, and

01:07:16.720 --> 01:07:19.630
celebrities

01:07:19.640 --> 01:07:21.950
because man will let you down. Jesus

01:07:21.960 --> 01:07:24.350
will never let you down.

01:07:24.360 --> 01:07:27.070
Man will fail you; Jesus will never fail

01:07:27.080 --> 01:07:28.390
you.

01:07:28.400 --> 01:07:30.830
He's perfect and he loves you and he

01:07:30.840 --> 01:07:33.030
gave his life for you.

01:07:33.040 --> 01:07:35.150
And the moment we keep the main thing,

01:07:35.160 --> 01:07:37.390
we'll always be victorious. But if we

01:07:37.400 --> 01:07:39.590
get off and start getting weird,

01:07:39.600 --> 01:07:40.990
guess what?

01:07:41.000 --> 01:07:43.310
Correction will come.

01:07:43.320 --> 01:07:45.790
We have to keep our eyes on Jesus in

01:07:45.800 --> 01:07:49.150
these last days because many will

01:07:49.160 --> 01:07:50.950
see all these weird

01:07:50.960 --> 01:07:53.390
doctrines, doctrines of demons.

01:07:53.400 --> 01:07:55.550
Men will be swayed

01:07:55.560 --> 01:07:57.750
by doctrines of demons, and the Bible

01:07:57.760 --> 01:08:00.750
warned us it was coming.

01:08:00.760 --> 01:08:02.830
Many false prophets will rise.

01:08:05.960 --> 01:08:09.070
Don't allow yourself to be snared by

01:08:09.080 --> 01:08:11.790
false prophetic words and false

01:08:11.800 --> 01:08:14.270
teachings

01:08:14.280 --> 01:08:16.590
just because you see something. I

01:08:16.600 --> 01:08:18.430
told you they're going to perform

01:08:18.440 --> 01:08:20.550
miracles in the days ahead. They're

01:08:20.560 --> 01:08:22.269
going to raise the dead in the days

01:08:22.279 --> 01:08:24.590
ahead. And just because you see them

01:08:24.600 --> 01:08:27.309
perform a miracle and see signs and

01:08:27.319 --> 01:08:29.789
wonders in their ministry doesn't mean

01:08:29.799 --> 01:08:32.309
they're of God.

01:08:32.319 --> 01:08:33.630
You're going to have to know and have

01:08:33.640 --> 01:08:35.269
great discernment. Just because they

01:08:35.279 --> 01:08:38.430
walk in the supernatural...

01:08:38.440 --> 01:08:40.910
think about this: Pharaoh's

01:08:40.920 --> 01:08:42.910
men

01:08:42.920 --> 01:08:46.269
doing miracles and demonic stuff with their

01:08:46.279 --> 01:08:48.309
staffs and the snakes.

01:08:48.319 --> 01:08:50.950
They threw them down and Moses's snake ate

01:08:50.960 --> 01:08:53.390
theirs, but it didn't mean they couldn't

01:08:53.400 --> 01:08:55.870
perform the same kind of stuff,

01:08:55.880 --> 01:08:57.349
black magic, and the things they were

01:08:57.359 --> 01:08:58.710
doing.

01:08:58.720 --> 01:09:01.910
So be careful who you follow. Just

01:09:01.920 --> 01:09:04.550
because you see them do something,

01:09:04.560 --> 01:09:06.030
discern it.

01:09:06.040 --> 01:09:10.710
Be vigilant to

01:09:10.720 --> 01:09:13.670
filter in these last days because we're

01:09:13.680 --> 01:09:17.510
going to be snared if you don't.

01:09:17.520 --> 01:09:19.470
I don't care what they say. I don't care

01:09:19.480 --> 01:09:22.950
what they do. Always stay

01:09:22.960 --> 01:09:25.470
vertical and keep your eyes on Jesus.

01:09:25.470 --> 01:09:25.480
Keep

01:09:25.480 --> 01:09:27.070
him the main thing in these last

01:09:27.080 --> 01:09:29.990
days.

01:09:30.000 --> 01:09:32.910
If you don't, you're in trouble.

01:09:32.920 --> 01:09:36.990
We must keep Jesus first.

01:09:37.000 --> 01:09:39.510
And the Bible—back it up with the

01:09:39.520 --> 01:09:41.829
word. Read the word. Read it and read it

01:09:41.839 --> 01:09:43.670
some more. And the more you

01:09:43.680 --> 01:09:45.470
read it, the more you're going to know.

01:09:45.480 --> 01:09:47.070
The Bible says you'll know the truth and the

01:09:47.080 --> 01:09:49.390
truth will set you free.

01:09:49.400 --> 01:09:51.269
So we can't be following prophetic

01:09:51.269 --> 01:09:51.279
so-and-so

01:09:51.279 --> 01:09:52.870
all the

01:09:52.880 --> 01:09:54.790
time and saying, "That's it

01:09:54.800 --> 01:09:56.870
right there. That's set in

01:09:56.870 --> 01:09:56.880
stone."Find

01:09:56.880 --> 01:09:59.270
it. Read the word. Keep your eyes on

01:09:59.280 --> 01:10:01.630
him. If it witnesses with you in your

01:10:01.640 --> 01:10:03.750
spirit that we're in the last

01:10:03.760 --> 01:10:06.870
days, then fine,

01:10:06.880 --> 01:10:09.670
keep running with it. If not, judge it.

01:10:09.680 --> 01:10:12.190
Keep quiet and just be still. Don't be

01:10:12.200 --> 01:10:14.390
so quick to jump on AI and all these

01:10:14.400 --> 01:10:16.350
things that we're about to

01:10:16.350 --> 01:10:16.360
see—many

01:10:16.360 --> 01:10:17.630
things

01:10:17.640 --> 01:10:19.870
to snare us.

01:10:19.880 --> 01:10:22.030
I hope that helps you because I feel like

01:10:22.040 --> 01:10:25.390
there's so much

01:10:25.400 --> 01:10:28.550
idolizing and weirdness.

01:10:28.560 --> 01:10:30.990
"Erica said this, she

01:10:31.000 --> 01:10:32.590
has the blue eyes, she's

01:10:32.590 --> 01:10:32.600
Esther."I

01:10:32.600 --> 01:10:34.430
don't know if she's

01:10:34.440 --> 01:10:35.870
Esther; the Lord didn't give me

01:10:35.870 --> 01:10:35.880
that

01:10:35.880 --> 01:10:37.910
word.

01:10:37.920 --> 01:10:39.550
You can't ask him

01:10:39.550 --> 01:10:39.560
because

01:10:39.560 --> 01:10:42.790
he went home.

01:10:42.800 --> 01:10:44.670
All we know is we have a recording of

01:10:44.680 --> 01:10:46.790
him saying something.

01:10:46.800 --> 01:10:49.150
You have to just weigh things out and

01:10:49.160 --> 01:10:52.430
