01:11:03.480 --> 01:11:05.110
I said test in your own spirit and see

01:11:05.120 --> 01:11:06.990
if it

01:11:06.990 --> 01:11:07.000
witnesses

01:11:07.000 --> 01:11:09.870
with

01:11:09.870 --> 01:11:09.880
you.

01:11:09.880 --> 01:11:12.390
